<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Password Has Been Changed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .alert-box {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Password Updated Successfully</h1>
  </div>

  <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
  
  <div class="alert-box">
    <p>Your Roleplay Platform account password was successfully changed on {{changeDate}}.</p>
  </div>
  
  <p>If you made this change, you can safely disregard this email. The change has been completed successfully.</p>
  
  <p><strong>If you didn't make this change:</strong></p>
  <ol>
    <li>Your account may have been compromised.</li>
    <li>We recommend that you reset your password immediately using the "Forgot Password" feature.</li>
    <li>Consider enabling two-factor authentication for added security.</li>
  </ol>
  
  <p>For your security, this email was sent to all email addresses associated with your account.</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>The Roleplay Platform Security Team</p>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© {{currentYear}} Roleplay Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    // Add current date and year to the email
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      // Add current year to the footer
      const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
      const yearElements = document.getElementsByClassName('current-year');
      for (let i = 0; i < yearElements.length; i++) {
        yearElements[i].textContent = currentYear;
      }
      
      // Add current date to the change date
      const changeDateElements = document.getElementsByClassName('change-date');
      const options = { 
        weekday: 'long', 
        year: 'numeric', 
        month: 'long', 
        day: 'numeric',
        hour: '2-digit',
        minute: '2-digit',
        timeZoneName: 'short' 
      };
      const formattedDate = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', options);
      
      for (let i = 0; i < changeDateElements.length; i++) {
        changeDateElements[i].textContent = formattedDate;
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
